name: Thelia\Core\Event\TheliaEvents
short_desc: This class contains all Thelia events identifiers used by Thelia Core

ACTION.name: ACTION
ACTION.long_desc: Sent if no action are already present in Thelia action process ( see Thelia\Routing\Matcher\ActionMatcher)

CUSTOMER_LOGOUT.name: CUSTOMER_LOGOUT
CUSTOMER_LOGOUT.short_desc: Sent before the logout of the customer.

CUSTOMER_LOGIN.name: CUSTOMER_LOGIN
CUSTOMER_LOGIN.short_desc: Sent once the customer is successfully logged in.

CUSTOMER_UPDATEPROFIL.name: CUSTOMER_UPDATEPROFIL
CUSTOMER_UPDATEPROFIL.short_desc: sent on customer account update profil

LOST_PASSWORD.name: LOST_PASSWORD
LOST_PASSWORD.short_desc: sent when a customer need a new password

ADMIN_LOGOUT.name: ADMIN_LOGOUT
ADMIN_LOGOUT.short_desc: Sent before the logout of the administrator.

ADMIN_LOGIN.name: ADMIN_LOGIN
ADMIN_LOGIN.short_desc: Sent once the administrator is successfully logged in.

BEFORE_CREATECUSTOMER.name: BEFORE_CREATECUSTOMER
BEFORE_CREATECUSTOMER.short_desc: Sent once the customer creation form has been successfully validated, and before customer insertion in the database.

AFTER_CREATECUSTOMER.name: AFTER_CREATECUSTOMER
AFTER_CREATECUSTOMER.short_desc: Sent just after a successful insert of a new customer in the database.

BEFORE_UPDATECUSTOMER.name: BEFORE_UPDATECUSTOMER
BEFORE_UPDATECUSTOMER.short_desc: Sent once the customer change form has been successfully validated, and before customer update in the database.

AFTER_UPDATECUSTOMER.name: AFTER_UPDATECUSTOMER
AFTER_UPDATECUSTOMER.short_desc: Sent just after a successful update of a customer in the database.

ADDRESS_DEFAULT.name: ADDRESS_DEFAULT
ADDRESS_DEFAULT.short_desc: sent when an address is tag as default

CART_DUPLICATE.name: CART_DUPLICATE
CART_DUPLICATE.short_desc: sent when a new existing cat id duplicated.
CART_DUPLICATE.long_desc: This append when current customer is different from current cart

AFTER_CARTADDITEM.name: AFTER_CARTADDITEM
AFTER_CARTADDITEM.short_desc: sent when a new item is added to current cart

AFTER_CARTUPDATEITEM.name: AFTER_CARTUPDATEITEM
AFTER_CARTUPDATEITEM.short_desc: sent when a cart item is modify

DOCUMENT_CLEAR_CACHE.name: DOCUMENT_CLEAR_CACHE
DOCUMENT_CLEAR_CACHE.short_desc: Sent on image cache clear request

IMAGE_CLEAR_CACHE.name: IMAGE_CLEAR_CACHE
IMAGE_CLEAR_CACHE.short_desc: Sent on image cache clear request

BEFORE_CREATE_COUPON.name: BEFORE_CREATE_COUPON
BEFORE_CREATE_COUPON.short_desc: Sent just before a successful insert of a new Coupon in the database.

AFTER_CREATE_COUPON.name: AFTER_CREATE_COUPON
AFTER_CREATE_COUPON.short_desc: Sent just after a successful insert of a new Coupon in the database.

BEFORE_UPDATE_COUPON.name: BEFORE_UPDATE_COUPON
BEFORE_UPDATE_COUPON.short_desc: Sent just before a successful update of a new Coupon in the database.

AFTER_UPDATE_COUPON.name: AFTER_UPDATE_COUPON
AFTER_UPDATE_COUPON.short_desc: Sent just after a successful update of a new Coupon in the database.

COUPON_CONSUME.name: COUPON_CONSUME
COUPON_CONSUME.short_desc: Sent when attempting to use a Coupon

BEFORE_CONSUME_COUPON.name: BEFORE_CONSUME_COUPON
BEFORE_CONSUME_COUPON.short_desc: Sent just before an attempt to use a Coupon

AFTER_CONSUME_COUPON.name: AFTER_CONSUME_COUPON
AFTER_CONSUME_COUPON.short_desc: Sent just after an attempt to use a Coupon

COUPON_CONDITION_UPDATE.name: COUPON_CONDITION_UPDATE
COUPON_CONDITION_UPDATE.short_desc: Sent when attempting to update Coupon Condition

BEFORE_COUPON_CONDITION_UPDATE.name: BEFORE_COUPON_CONDITION_UPDATE
BEFORE_COUPON_CONDITION_UPDATE.short_desc: Sent just before an attempt to update a Coupon Condition

AFTER_COUPON_CONDITION_UPDATE.name: AFTER_COUPON_CONDITION_UPDATE
AFTER_COUPON_CONDITION_UPDATE.short_desc: Sent just after an attempt to update a Coupon Condition

MAILTRANSPORTER_CONFIG.name: MAILTRANSPORTER_CONFIG
MAILTRANSPORTER_CONFIG.short_desc: sent when system find a mailer transporter.

GENERATE_REWRITTENURL.name: GENERATE_REWRITTENURL
GENERATE_REWRITTENURL.short_desc: sent when Thelia try to generate a rewriten url

MODULE_TOGGLE_ACTIVATION.name: MODULE_TOGGLE_ACTIVATION
MODULE_TOGGLE_ACTIVATION.short_desc: sent when a module is activated or deactivated

MODULE_DELETE.name: MODULE_DELETE
MODULE_DELETE.short_desc: sent when a module is deleted

NEWSLETTER_SUBSCRIBE.name: NEWSLETTER_SUBSCRIBE
NEWSLETTER_SUBSCRIBE.short_desc: sent for subscribing to the newsletter
